Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.54,0:00:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind's gotten cold,\Nhasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with her?\NShe's pretty unsociable today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.23,0:00:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going\Nhome now, Anna?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The restaurants in this area\Nare already closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.56,0:01:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back to the hotel, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.24,0:01:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.37,0:01:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason,\Nthe people on this street know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.41,0:01:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They call me "Anna."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Suk is a suspect in\Na multiple homicide case,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't see any\Npolice or police cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm going to\Ncheck on the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Whatever the case,\NI've got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.94,0:03:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same inside.\NThere's no sign of the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. There's an injured man\Nnamed Suk being hospitalized here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Jan Suk... He's a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:03:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:04:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There were a lot of injured men at\Nthe abandoned building on Bruno Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. One of those unemployed men\Nwho were injured in the fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Unemployed? Fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.73,0:04:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what they\Nwere saying on the news,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's probably the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And? What room are\Nthey in right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They had terrible wounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but after we treated them, they were\Nall moved to a different hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.51,0:04:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Moved to a different hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.48,0:04:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? An ambulance came\Nand loaded up all six of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.98,0:04:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There were six men\Nwho attacked us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.82,0:04:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Suk?\NWhere's Detective Jan Suk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.66,0:04:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He was shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There weren't any patients brought in\Nwith gunshot wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then is there any record of a patient\Nbrought in with the name Jan Suk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,None at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Research data concerning\N511 Kinderheim and a tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:04:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.51,0:05:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A former director of 511 Kinderheim,\Nnamed Pedrov,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,gave it to me before he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.29,0:05:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He was running an illegal orphanage\Nin Prague.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would be after it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure that the former\NCzechoslovakian secret police are after it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.97,0:05:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the data\Nand the tape right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have it with me.\NI'm keeping it in a certain location.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.71,0:05:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective Suk was seriously injured\Nand was kidnapped from the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know what they'll do to Suk\Nto get what they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How depressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The data and the contents\Nof the tape.. . What are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The research data was\Na list of technical terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There was also a list of names.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.30,0:05:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't examine it closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I only listened to\Nthe main parts of the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it a recording of?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.51,0:05:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A child's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.78,0:06:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A child?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He was probably drugged,\Nthen questioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When asked what his name was,\Nhe answered, "Johan."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Doctor Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,511 Kinderheim...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Research data...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the tape right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.34,0:06:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Suk?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.61,0:06:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this in\Na business-like manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Suk?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.98,0:06:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.49,0:06:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving me aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.02,0:06:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Tenma, you don't need\Nto get involved any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I also have something I want to\Nask the Czechoslovakian secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the question is whether we\Ncan negotiate with these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.02,0:07:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not inviting us to dinner,\Nare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome. ..\NCome right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That man...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, he's an important figure\Nwith the Czechoslovakian secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I looked him up at\Nthe newspaper company.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Karel Lanke...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So the big boss\Nhas finally appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry that my subordinates\Nwere rough with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.29,0:07:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This unintended situation was the result\Nof an error within our chain of command.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:08:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We have been terribly\Nmisunderstood... by you and the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We're viewed as\Na gang of killers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Suk?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He's at one of our hospitals.\NHis life isn't in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired of people telling me\Nthat this is a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.71,0:08:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't killed anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What about that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that blonde woman\Nacting on your orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've received information on her,\Nbut she isn't involved with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been quite\Nan inconvenience to us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.96,0:08:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want peoples' lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A German friend wanted\Nthat tape and the data.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been carefully\Nnegotiating with Pedrov.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when he was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There must have been\Na lot of money involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. This is a business.\NI just want to talk business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I want that tape and data\Nin return for Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not talk like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.43,0:09:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We mustn't let that\Nhappen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If such a thing was in the world,\Nwho knows what would happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We mustn't let that happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not talk about things\Nlike that for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.68,0:09:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have anything to do\Nwith our current discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a graduate\Nof 511 Kinderheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you leave that place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.97,0:09:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I was supposedly fourteen,\Nbut that was 30 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.81,0:09:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,When were you placed there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:09:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?\NI was probably seven or eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Around 1963, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know this boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He's my nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In the early 60s,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.40,0:10:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I was officially stationed in Berlin\Nas an intelligence officer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,for the Czechoslovakian\Nambassador.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a younger sister.\NShe married a German.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But my younger sister\Nand her husband
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.01,0:10:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,plotted to defect and\Ncross the Berlin Wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They were shot dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Their child was all that\Nwas left of their family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I signed him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that it was\Na wonderful place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.63,0:10:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,An ideal educational environment\Nto educate children with dubious pasts
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,into the future communist elite.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:11:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I signed him up to be put\Ninto 511 Kinderheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.19,0:11:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't remember what happened\Nthere or what happened before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.96,0:11:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even remember\Nmy real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.23,0:11:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to make money\Non something horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to sell\Nthe information
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that includes experimental data\Non your own nephew!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.28,0:11:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got off topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to approach this\Nin a business-like manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.19,0:11:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You may leave for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I await a favorable response.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give these gentlemen\Na courteous farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.01,0:12:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, saving Suk\Nis what's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.51,0:12:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he'll release Suk if\Nwe give him what he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot Cocoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.53,0:12:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.97,0:12:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Our weekly hot cocoa... He\Nlooked forward to getting hot cocoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,When I got a fever and\Nslept in the infirmary,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,he brought me hot cocoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,His hot cocoa.. .\NEven though he liked it so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It was delicious. It was the first time\NI had hot cocoa that was so delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So I wanted to thank him\Nin some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.27,0:13:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when he said,\N"remember me."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, we all did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.01,0:13:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We talked about each other\Nto our friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know why,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.12,0:13:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but our memories would fade\Nday-by-day at these strange lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We could hardly\Nremember our names.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why.. .\NThat's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We had our friends\Nremember who we were!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He loved hot cocoa,\Ndrawing pictures, and bugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But he didn't like bug collections\Nbecause you have to kill the bugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The most enjoyable\Ntime he had
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.48,0:13:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,was when he went to the forest\Nwith his parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He caught\Na lot of butterflies!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But when he went home, he let\Nthe butterflies out of the bug cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:13:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,His dream was to\Nbecome an entomologist!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.99,0:14:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,His...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,His name was Adolf Reinhart!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Welcome home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't keep secrets from him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}People can become\Nanything they want to be.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.18,0:15:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cheers!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, welcome home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.79,0:15:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, welcome home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, welcome home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.07,0:15:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.47,0:15:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The road leading up to here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This scenery...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This sign...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.18,0:15:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I know all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you also know this door?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:15:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.26,0:16:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I also know these stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer,\NI thought about this all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something\NI want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Tenma... That tape and\Nthe data have nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.32,0:16:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like we don't\Nhave time to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.39,0:16:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They seem like they\Ncan't wait to negotiate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The former Czechoslovakian\Nsecret police...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.33,0:16:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Have taken the time\Nto make an appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you thought\Neverything through?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:17:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I don't plan on handing over\Nthe tape and the research data.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying that you don't care\Nwhat happens to Detective Suk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If something\Nhappens to Suk,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.91,0:17:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that tape and data will disappear\Nfrom this world forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.12,0:17:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's stop with such\Ntrifling exchanges.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.19,0:17:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll let you listen to the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My condition is that\Nyou forget doing business
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,with the German friend\Nwho you plan on selling it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you listen to the tape\Nif you want to listen to it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you should listen to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.51,0:17:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,For your nephew who was sent\Nto 511 Kinderheim, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.02,0:17:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You should listen to Johan,\Nthe boy on the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.89,0:17:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that your deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.99,0:17:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not making a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:17:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.46,0:18:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's not the time\Nto be doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,As we speak, someone might be\Nkilled because of that tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people involved with\Nthe Czechoslovakian secret police
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.91,0:18:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,have been killed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think killed them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.98,0:18:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who wants\Nthe tape the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The person whose voice\Nwas recorded.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.02,0:18:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what\Nyou're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.83,0:18:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't act dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Your German friend should have\Ntold you what kind of tape it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he tell you to obtain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Monster's Identity."\NThat's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to get you involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll tell you everything.\NBefore anyone else is killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:18:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So Johan has come to Prague\Nin search of his roots.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. He might be\Ntrying to erase of all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world did you\Ndo to him 15 years ago?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A mother and her child lived near\NCedok Bridge in the Mikalska District.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.98,0:19:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, they were taken away\Nby the secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do to Johan
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,when you took him from the building\Nwith the sign with three frogs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,These stairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Big brother...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragged down these steps\Nand taken away...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.45,0:19:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.72,0:20:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed,\Nduring that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in a position where I could\Nget all the information I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.09,0:20:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But the three frogs. ..\NTaking away a mother and child...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't act dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.13,0:20:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, there was information\Nthat even I didn't receive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Things that man did...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.63,0:20:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't know which branch\Nof the secret police he belonged to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Or even what chain of\Ncommand he followed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.48,0:20:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He could freely detain many people\Nfor whatever reason without reporting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What was he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He was only a captain, but he was\Ngranted a luxurious mansion to work in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.16,0:20:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He was called\N"the Man of Red Rose Mansion."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying\Nthat man was involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.57,0:20:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a very elegant\Nand quiet man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:21:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't wear a uniform\Nand liked tea and cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.84,0:21:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that man's name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.68,0:21:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz. .. Bonaparta...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't know if it was his\Nreal name. He used a pseudonym.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.52,0:21:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A pseudonym?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.89,0:21:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He also wrote picture books.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.10,0:21:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you afraid of this door?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.97,0:21:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I was reading\Na picture book in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.61,0:21:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The door opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.21,0:21:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.52,0:21:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Picture book?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.56,0:21:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It was a strange picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.89,0:21:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It was called,\N{\i1}The Nameless Monster.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.06,0:21:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing here, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.34,0:22:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.07,0:22:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I was reading\Na picture book here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.64,0:22:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But the one who opened the door\Nand came back.. .was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I was greeting myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.23,0:22:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Welcome home.{\i0}
